➜广西诗人陈熠明：花飞影落醉婵娟
http://www.sohu.com/a/418178751_100115135	57996
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200914/e74bbaec4ec840068b38204fe420436e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>花飞影落醉婵娟</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（一）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•云中玉女散花来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">烟飞影幻瑶台上，笑面银河浪里开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">碧宇长天星海梦，云中玉女散花来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（二）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•花飞梦外落云风</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">银河曲韵浪潮生，望远天边月影成。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">玉女翩翩姿影幻，花飞梦外落云风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（三）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•笑面长风落雨花</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">送暖人间万户家，流云有梦在天涯。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吉祥善上飞如意，笑面长风落雨花。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200914/0edb6f070d874d3ebdec9f21f8fd5f0a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
